# ReBAC × Cedar (embedded) — document → folder → org-unit → ancestor-unit graph
# Membership at a parent company grants visibility into subsidiaries' documents.
# ~5% of folders are additionally shared with a second unit of the same tenant (fan-in).

@host = http://localhost:8080

### ALLOW — persona is a member at the doc's org (or an ancestor / shared unit)
POST {{host}}/v1/authorize
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "engine": "cedar",
  "model": "rebac",
  "principal": "psn-511178",
  "action": "doc.view",
  "resource_type": "RebacDocument",
  "resource": "rdoc-000303"
}

### DENY — a different persona with no relationship path to the same document
POST {{host}}/v1/authorize
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "engine": "cedar",
  "model": "rebac",
  "principal": "psn-641800",
  "action": "doc.view",
  "resource_type": "RebacDocument",
  "resource": "rdoc-000303"
}
